{"tid":2500599,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人鍾意睇一啲冇恐怖鏡頭宗教恐怖片","createTime":"2021-04-22T18:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T11:48:04.000Z","uid":132174,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"842d29156eb71a155a3b200aca2b875a41b9bde5","tid":2500599,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T18:57:34.000Z","msg":"最近接觸到一套電影叫 Saint Maud<br />\n主角因為冇朋友所以用宗教去慰藉自己心靈<br />\n跟住發現只係自己呃自己 最後思覺失調聽到天父召喚而自焚<br />\n<br />\n全程冇一個恐怖鏡頭 但係拍攝手法令人壓抑到爆<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeYwH5eCANnZziVhLb9MtAWDtLkLg8MWhQYSnKXFEnkUp?filename=rEA6rLL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrEA6rLL.jpg&h=212ce95c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有講邪教嘅Hereditary 同 Midsommar <br />\n又係冇咩恐怖鏡頭 但係演員用表情就已經足夠令人好不安<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmapDw1RrvFqbRDBFyLTy4PyRs5qGuyKLXMeZaBMndo5aH?filename=Nd2sVEr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNd2sVEr.png&h=3de314bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRg2xgbipJBR3UNTbt19Th8DUAdiBC7FkswSRinbiUzyS?filename=DoijML6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDoijML6.png&h=4e75759b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢類型電影恐怖在於 佢講述一個正常人 佢哋受到打擊 之後決定投靠信仰 再為咗迎合信仰去扭曲自己人格<br />\n<br />\n成個心路歷程會令人覺得好壓抑 同埋產生一種自我懷疑<br />\n<br />\n睇完之後會禁不住反問 如果有一日遭受到好似主角嘅遭遇 自己又會唔會好似佢哋咁墮落？"},{"pid":"a49677e5b1e051163140167a92197363e5565520","tid":2500599,"uid":331821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T19:03:58.000Z","msg":"Fedora tipping atheism was cool 5 years ago"},{"pid":"4021211d4a468a39bb7be50e1f1557fdfafe98d3","tid":2500599,"uid":59014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T19:32:32.000Z","msg":"The Wicker Man<br />\nRosemary's Baby<br />\nThe Omen"},{"pid":"b93dc4ca8f208183e8bb6937fbb467e7e96d9855","tid":2500599,"uid":341722,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T20:28:18.000Z","msg":"第一套睇完靜左一陣諗其實自己都係咁孤獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後一陣就聽日要返既念頭出返黎又無事"},{"pid":"de9e7784230d7986a135b7040d5899284264a950","tid":2500599,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T21:04:26.000Z","msg":"jennifer lawrence套mother!算唔算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我勁唔鐘意<br />\n係就係充滿隱喻幾得意<br />\n但睇完好似冇睇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617dc08e1adf585574dce351997e1d89834da878","tid":2500599,"uid":364767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T22:27:17.000Z","msg":"太多血腥恐怖鏡頭 只會得啖笑<br />\n試過係戲院睇垃圾恐怖片，全院哄堂大笑<br />\n高評價恐怖片都冇乜血腥或音響警嚇鏡頭<br />\n例如:The Omen,Amityville horror"},{"pid":"6cbe394e4774831d85b389b9b67114287b72246c","tid":2500599,"uid":188282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T22:52:52.000Z","msg":"果套法國嘅旬道者令人極度忿怒"},{"pid":"564d6bf7ebce2d06d2e6839a938d420b5c61ae9c","tid":2500599,"uid":2737,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T23:26:25.000Z","msg":"好鍾意呢啲 一時間諗到有the killing of a sacred deer"},{"pid":"1235e818d040e5fc93d4cd05ac0bdf5e3ab84221","tid":2500599,"uid":240890,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T00:27:54.000Z","msg":"無記錯<br />\nHereditary 同 Midsommar係同一導演<br />\n我鍾意midsommor 多啲<br />\nHereditary 有啲深 睇完都唔知發生咩事"},{"pid":"18c4db48ebce08594f98a2d0aade6b7d966214b3","tid":2500599,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T00:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d5553391f2a06b5f31f7098c0cb88561361adf","tid":2500599,"uid":240890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021